      "visualDescription": "A vibrant 2D anime illustration depicting the full cycle of growth. In the foreground, a tiny, glowing brown seed is nestled in rich soil, with a delicate green seedling just emerging next to it. Dominating the middle ground is a majestic, towering tree with a wide green canopy, providing shade. Its strong roots are visible, anchoring it firmly. The background features soft, rolling green hills under a warm, gentle sun. The overall mood is peaceful, hopeful, and highlights nature's power and growth. Clean line art, warm soft lighting, expressive natural beauty.",
      "dialogueOrNarration": "A tiny seed sleeps deep in the earth. It is very small. [pause] Rain waters it. The sun warms it. Slowly, the seed takes food from the soil. It starts to change. A little green sprout comes out. It pushes up to the light. The sprout becomes a small plant. It grows taller every day. Its roots go deep into the ground. Its branches reach for the sky. Time passes. The small plant becomes a big, strong tree. It gives cool shade. Birds find a home there. It shows the power of nature. [warmly] It is a beautiful tree.",
      "subtitle": "A tiny seed sleeps deep in the earth. It is very small. Rain waters it. The sun warms it. Slowly, the seed takes food from the soil. It starts to change. A little green sprout comes out. It pushes up to the light. The sprout becomes a small plant. It grows taller every day. Its roots go deep into the ground. Its branches reach for the sky. Time passes. The small plant becomes a big, strong tree. It gives cool shade. Birds find a home there. It shows the power of nature. It is a beautiful tree.\nMột hạt giống nhỏ bé nằm sâu trong lòng đất. Nó rất nhỏ. Mưa tưới nó. Mặt trời làm ấm nó. Dần dần, hạt giống hút thức ăn từ đất. Nó bắt đầu thay đổi. Một mầm xanh nhỏ nhú lên. Nó vươn lên ánh sáng. Mầm non trở thành một cây con. Nó cao lớn hơn mỗi ngày. Rễ của nó bám sâu vào lòng đất. Cành của nó vươn tới bầu trời. Thời gian trôi qua. Cây con trở thành một cái cây lớn, mạnh mẽ. Nó mang lại bóng mát dễ chịu. Chim chóc tìm thấy tổ ấm ở đó. Nó thể hiện sức mạnh của thiên nhiên. Đó là một cái cây đẹp.",
